title: INDONESIA PRESS-Kalbe Farma Q3 net profit up 10 pct y/y - Kontan
description: Drugmaker PT Kalbe Farma reported a net profit of 1.36 trillion rupiah ($122 million) in the third quarter of 2013, up 10 percent from a year earlier.
